<section>
    <h3 class="text-center mb-4 pb-2 text-primary fw-bold">FAQ</h3>
    <p class="text-center mb-5">
        Frequently Asked Questions
    </p>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
            <h6 class="mb-3 text-primary"> What days can I rent a dumpster?</h6>
            <p>
                Dumpsters are available for delivery Mondays and Thursdays.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
            <h6 class="mb-3 text-primary"> When will my dumpster be delivered?</h6>
            <p>
                Dumpster will be delivered anytime between 7:30 AM to 3:00 PM. 
                We cannot guaruntee specific delivery times.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
            <h6 class="mb-3 text-primary">How many times can I rent a dumpster?</h6>
            <p>
                Residents are limited to one (1) dumpster rental up to three (3) times per calendar year.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
            <h6 class="mb-3 text-primary">I don't live in Draper, can I rent a dumpster?</h6>
            <p>
                No, the dumpster rental program is restricted to addresses within Draper, Utah only.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
            <h6 class="mb-3 text-primary">Can I rent a dumpster for a group?</h6>
            <p>
                Yes, neighborhood groups, HOAs, and volunteer groups located within Draper City are 
                limited to Monday delivery only and are limited to no more than four (4) dumpster rentals
                at a time, up to two (2) times per calendar year.
            </p>
        </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
            <h6 class="mb-3 text-primary">What sizes of dumpster do you offer?</h6>
            <p>
                We offer two sizes of dumpster:
                <ul>
                    <li>20-Yard - $120 rental fee (16' L x 6' H x 8' W, weight limit 6 tons)</li>
                    <li>30-Yard - $150 rental fee (22' L x 6' H x 8' W, weight limit 10 tons)</li>
                </ul>
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
            <h6 class="mb-3 text-primary">What is your cancellation policy?</h6>
            <p>
                Cancellations must be made at least five (5) days before the delivery date to get a refund. 
                All cancellations will be charged a $10 bookkeeping fee.
            </p>
        </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
            <h6 class="mb-3 text-primary">What am I allowed to put in the dumpster?</h6>
            <p>
                The dumpster may be used for yard debris (tree limbs, shrubbery, grass clippings, etc.) as well 
                as building materials, household items, some appliances, furniture, etc. Items that are not acceptable 
                in the dumpster are toxic, harardous or flammable materials such as pesticides, herbicides, solvents, 
                chemicals, paints, motor oil, gasoline, etc. Also, tires, batteries, freezers and refrigerators, and 
                metal or platic drums (unless the tops are cut off) may not be deposited in the dumpster. Please call 
                385-468-3862 for hazardous wastes disposal. The responsible party signing for the dumpster will be liable 
                for the illegal placement of these items or any spillage from overloading the dumpster.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>